data.description: This is exactly what you have been looking for! This beautiful 4 sided brick ranch with huge finished basement.   As you enter the main level, the foyer has Italian marble flooring. This home has 18 foot trey ceilings. All bathrooms have been updated with new toilets, walk in frameless glass showers, vanities and floors. Open concept, beautiful kitchen with floating shelves, rustic cabinetry and a large walk in pantry. Updated stainless steel appliances. Huge living room featuring an accent wood plank wall with custom floating shelves and the first fireplace. Oversized bedrooms with large master on the main. Completely updated spa like master bath, walk in closet with custom storage. Large updated laundry room with stained shelves, closet and laundry sink. Main floor has large sunroom, tiled with large windows and relax next to the second fireplace. Full finished basement has 3 entrances, full eat in kitchen, updated full bath, large bedrooms and living room with the third fireplace. Back yard is sitting on almost an acre. New beautiful deck to enjoy your large level fenced in backyard. Plenty of room to add anything you want, future pool, outdoor firepit or even a playground. Words can not describe how this home is everything you need to call your own. Call today before it slips away! Agent owned.     No showings until April 29, 2024.
